  "description": "A breathtaking aerial view captures a dramatic coastal landscape bathed in the warm glow of either sunrise or sunset. The sky is dominated by large, billowing cumulus clouds, some appearing dark and shadowed while others are illuminated with golden light. A vibrant burst of rainbow colors is subtly visible within the cloud formation. Below, a calm body of water stretches towards the horizon, with landmasses visible in the distance including rolling hills and a long bridge structure, suggesting an urban or developed coastline. Lush green trees occupy the foreground, partially obscuring the view of the city below. The overall composition evokes a sense of grandeur and natural beauty.",
